<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-39-1199 </DOCNO><TEXT>A first listing of the heat pumps used in industrial processing (excludingair conditioning) leads to a global estimate of 5.000 to 6.000 units,corresponding to a 100.000 kW total power. Among these 300 have a powerof more than 30 kW each and represent half of the total implemented power.The heat pumps are mainly used for wood drying, thermo-vinification,heating of conservatories and malting. Market forecasts, favourable forseveral classical or new applications are being strenghened by technologicalinnovations.</TEXT></DOC>